Class RoomsTuple<ArrayList,List>

java.lang.Object
structures.RoomsTuple<ArrayList,List>
public class RoomsTuple<ArrayList,List> extends Object
The RoomsTuple class represents a tuple containing two elements: a list of room line data and a list of room column headers.
